@@TJvScrollTextDirection
<TITLE TJvScrollTextDirection type>
Summary
  Enumerates ways text can scroll on a control.
Description
  Use the TJvScrollTextDirection type to specify how text should scroll on a control.
@@TJvScrollTextDirection.drFromLeft
  Text is scrolled from left to right.
@@TJvScrollTextDirection.drFromRight
  Text is scrolled from right to left.
@@TJvScrollTextDirection.drFromTop
  Text is scrolled from top to bottom.
@@TJvScrollTextDirection.drFromBottom
  Text is scrolled from bottom to top.
